<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>404 - Halaman Tidak Ditemukan | Kudayu</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/kudayu/favicon.svg" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

  <main class="not-found">
    <div class="wrapper">
      <!-- Left: Content -->
      <div class="content">
        <div class="error-badge">Error 404</div>
        <div class="error-code">404</div>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <h1>Halaman Tidak Ditemukan</h1>
        <p class="description">
          Sepertinya kuda yang Anda cari sudah berlari jauh.<br>
          Halaman ini tidak ada, sudah dipindahkan, atau URL yang dimasukkan salah.
        </p>
        <div class="actions">
          <a href="/kudayu/" class="btn-primary">← Kembali ke Beranda</a>
          <a href="/kudayu/horses" class="btn-secondary">Lihat Katalog Kuda</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: GIF -->
      <div class="visual">
        <div class="gif-frame">
          <img src="/kudayu/haru-urara-uraraharu.gif" alt="Haru Urara" />
        </div>
        <p class="gif-caption">404 berarti admin lagi jalan-jalan sama Haru urara</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Contact box below grid -->
    <div class="contact-bar">
      <span class="contact-label">🛠 Butuh bantuan?</span>
      <p>
        Jika Anda yakin ini adalah kesalahan sistem, silakan hubungi admin kami di
        <a href="mailto:drawingtogether21@gmail.com">drawingtogether21@gmail.com</a>
        dengan menyertakan URL halaman atau screenshot yang Anda kunjungi.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>

</body>
</html>

<style>
  body {
    font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    background: #0A0A0A;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .not-found {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .not-found::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 50% at 30% 60%, rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.12) 0%, transparent 70%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 40% at 70% 30%, rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .wrapper {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    max-width: 960px;
    width: 100%;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .content { text-align: left; }

  .error-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background: rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.35);
    color: #FF6B6B;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .error-badge::before {
    content: '';
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: #FF6B6B;
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: blink 1.4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes blink {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.2; }
  }

  .error-code {
    font-size: clamp(5rem, 12vw, 8rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFFFFF 0%, #C0C0C0 40%, #FFFFFF 70%, #DC143C 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    background-size: 200% auto;
    animation: glossySweep 4s linear infinite;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  @keyframes glossySweep {
    0% { background-position: 0% center; }
    100% { background-position: 200% center; }
  }

  .divider {
    width: 40px;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #DC143C, #FFD700);
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 3vw, 1.75rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .description {
    color: #888;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    background: #DC143C;
    color: #FFFFFF;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.3);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #b01030;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.45);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    color: #CCCCCC;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    color: #FFFFFF;
  }

  .contact-bar {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 960px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.75rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .contact-label {
    display: block;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    padding-top: 0.15rem;
  }

  .contact-bar p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .contact-bar a {
    color: #FFD700;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .contact-bar a:hover { color: #FFE84D; }

  .visual {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .gif-frame {
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow:
      0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08),
      0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6),
      0 0 80px rgba(220, 20, 60, 0.15);
  }

  .gif-frame img {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 340px;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 20px;
  }

  .gif-caption {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #444;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 680px) {
    .wrapper { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    .content { text-align: center; }
    .error-badge { justify-content: center; }
    .actions { justify-content: center; }
    .divider { margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
    .visual { order: -1; }
    .gif-frame img { max-width: 220px; }
  }
</style>
